  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Adds parcels of land to the list of premises which are exempt from the provisions of law which generally restrict manufacturers/wholesalers and retailers from sharing an interest in a liquor license."
